lor=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 10:10:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Best taunt spells for agro maintenance</span><hr size=1> I use flash of light a lot.  It's extremely effective and the mana cost is nothing.  What do the rest of you use?<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uharlan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Harlan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 10:20:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> stuns</span><hr size=1> All of the stuns are great. Careful with flash - if it isn't resisted and the MOB's target is not in melee range he'll go running off randomly.<br>
<br>
All stuns are great. In fact, Cease and desist might be the best because they don't stun the MOB for long enough for the aggro of landing the spell to decay. Stun is great for allowing rogues the moment of calm required to evade successfully.<br>
<br>
Harlan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwarasen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>warasen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 10:23:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best taunt spells for agro maintenance</span><hr size=1> Stuns and Flame of Light. Stun is a fast cast and is a nice aggro. If I'm not the puller I usually try and time my first stun to hit just as the mob reaches the camp and I usually chain it about 3 times mixing in taunts and I'll have aggro for the rest of the fight. To break mez I use Root, taunt, flash, taunt, flame of light and stun before I even hit the attack key. Flash is resisted alot and doesn't last long if it mob isn't tashed. I find Stun builds aggro even on giants so I load it still. Flame of Light is great in Kael <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Warasen Durendel<br>
Knight of the Imperial Guardians<br>
Mith Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukeldal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>keldal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 10:50:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best taunt spells for agro maintenance</span><hr size=1> The two new stuns are fantastic.  They piss the mob off but don't freeze the mob in place...I always feel bad taunting a mob that's stuck on the rogue with a long-lasting stun 'cause it may cost the rogue a BS &amp; that backstab is probably a hell of a lot better than the uber damage that force puts out <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I mostly use stuns for spell interrupts during soloing.  Cease &amp; desist are a lot less of a mana drain than our later stuns &amp; with that new haste buff mana is getting scarce.<br>
<br>
--Keldal <p><p><P><CENTER><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~jasonandali/Images/sigsmall.jpg"></CENTER><br><center>"Has anybody got a plan?"<br> 
 -G.A. Custer</center></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugilfalas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilfalas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 11:28:58 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best taunt spells for agro maintenance</span><hr size=1> The 3 cheap mana cost stuns of Cease, Desist and Stun are our best tools for generating aggro fast and controlling it and the spell Divine Aura is great for instantly bleeding off aggro.<br>
<br>
Paladins can really aggro control like a maestro if they know there stuff. <p><center>
