 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uashrammdamodred.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ashramm Damodred</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 9:17:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best taunt spells for agro maintenance</span><hr size=1> I realize now that if i ever hit tov .. i'll probably need a diff weapon than epic .. some of you might be crying foul that anyone would ever put an epic away .. but anyone that has one knows 2 things.. epic proc = nasty taunt then add  divine might = uber uber uber taunt .. I've done plane raids where the only thing i did was have divine might up and haste + my epic .. I never hit disarm .. or taunt .. and a quite a few times the mob would turn to me and hit me just because of a double proc .. even if it was 2 divine mights .. or a divine might/holy shock combo .. Epic + Divine might + haste = agro machine.  I used to fight for agro in exp groups when I was MA .. that all changed once I got epic.  I rarely have to hit taunt anymore and I'm usually FM cause I don't have to stun even 1/4 as much as I did before ..  <p>Ashramm Damodred<br>53 Epic Cavalier of Tunare<br>Talon Zek<br>
